snippet.title: Heavy Duty Challenge | PreRelease Trailer
snippet.description:
The Ultimate Off-Road Truck Experience - Coming September 14 | https://store.steampowered.com/app/1165530/Heavy_Duty_Challenge_The_OffRoad_Truck_Simulator/

Drive powerful trucks and explore open world environments. Master your skills and win truck trial championships.​ Experience off-road driving like never before! 

For more news and information follow us:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HeavyDutyChallenge
Twitter: https://twitter.com/HDCthegame
